<br>
Overlord Faeolin, I did not mean to seem pert. Though working with you shall be a challenge, I am willing to take it, for my feelings in this aren't of importance. Please note that I know one of your ranks well. He is known as Daiunus Darkenvalor and has the title of Dread Harvester. He knows me best as Kildaili. Maybe you would like to fill him in on this, and see if he has any suggestions. He knows how difficult I can be. Just a thought...Good Evening.<br>
<br>
*Smiling slightly, Damia puts away her quill, closes the book and walks out of the room*<br>
<br>
